          "speaker": "Speaker_Homer",
          "text": "Within a green-tinged chamber that the shrilly-singing Sirens made their own, a pathway plunges deep into the unknown outskirts of the Underworld."
        }
      ],
      "endLines": [
        {
          "speaker": "PlayerUnit",
          "text": "So this is Scylla's little lair, huh?"
